HB Draft 2026 Regular Session
Abstract: Provides relative to permits for in-state manufacturing distillers producing less
than 100 gallons.
Present law provides that the commissioner of the office of alcohol and tobacco control may
issue a permit for a fee to entities in the business of manufacturing, supplying, or dealing in
alcoholic beverages.
